{"tid":357020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"寫\"Chinglish\" 嘅偽abc入一入黎","createTime":"2017-08-12T14:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-12T14:55:16.000Z","uid":133665,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"57b54c93a6b9af20d32b0bb89a6a9b5e0f3c7085","tid":357020,"uid":133665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"中文就中文，英文就英文，<br />\n成日又ngo 又nei都唔知你講乜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/12/222429_52c5f2d589abf5b636986a877e2497bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F12%2F222429_52c5f2d589abf5b636986a877e2497bd.jpg&h=b7aa6f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為自己係外國讀過兩年書識少少英文，<br />\n就圍來整個on9語言出黎，得啲所謂&quot;自己人&quot;先睇得明，完全表現出想融入小圈子嘅自卑心態，有少少文化嘅人見到都覺得好肉酸。<br />\n<br />\n有人話打chinglish 快過打中文字，我就唔信打筆畫同速成會慢好多，總好過用啲唔3唔4嘅垃圾語言。<br />\n<br />\n繁體字有本身獨特嘅意思，係香港人就寫返繁體，如果連自己都唔識尊重自己嘅語言，我唔會尊重你。"},{"pid":"aad1b28b733ff673765a79820147820696419463","tid":357020,"uid":56795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"有朋友打chinglish真係好快 幾分鐘 成篇出咗嚟"},{"pid":"cbc4bd397a5f20b0608d5176b65d4b1d22704da4","tid":357020,"uid":76098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:31:03.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩就做乜鳩啦， 做咩改自己叫jm9?"},{"pid":"fe35c4deeb9dc44347acae5374457958f6ac47df","tid":357020,"uid":83165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:35:59.000Z","msg":"樓主係文探花 ？"},{"pid":"8f770975421a4e8f048229afd09a2060f1ca571b","tid":357020,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"我真係睇唔明佢寫乜tim.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894077ab46c816304e7d169c0196e65eef834471","tid":357020,"uid":135170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T14:47:54.000Z","msg":"你 giu ngo?"},{"pid":"1f44635b03522ce626390c33c12166e47722836f","tid":357020,